<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">س ف ط:</span> <span class="c2">(السَّفَطُ)</span> وَاحِدُ <span class="c2">(الْأَسْفَاطِ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(الْإِسْفَنْطُ)</span> ضَرْبٌ مِنَ الْأَشْرِبَةِ فَارِسِيٌّ مُعَرَّبٌ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ الْأَصْمَعِيُّ:</span> هُوَ بِالرُّومِيَّةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>